title: Grateful Dead Live at Henry J. Kaiser Auditorium on 1988-02-14
description:
One  	Touch Of Gray ; Feel Like A Stranger > Franklin's Tower > Walkin' Blues ; When Push Comes To Shove ; Cassidy 
Two 	China Cat Sunflower > I Know You Rider ; Samson and Delilah ; Terrapin Station > Drums > Space> I Need A Miracle > Stella Blue > Throwing Stones > Turn On Your Lovelight 
Encore 	The Mighty Quinn

reviews.review_text: Great Recording - Memorable Show Wow.. I just found this site.. not sure how, but so glad I did... what memories!!!  I remember going to this show with an old friend.. It had been sold out for weeks, we were like a good day's drive away, but just went on the spur of the moment w/o tickets.  Some girl gave my friend one almost right away, I had a sign said, "I need a miracle ticket".. someone of the GD staff came out & gave me a complimentary ticket... was Valentine's day.. only was there for that one show.. but OMG!  It was incridible... thanks for sharing your excellent recording!  :)
